data.label: Gio
data.description: Gio是一个用于编写跨平台即时模式GUI的Go语言库。Gio支持所有主要平台：Linux、macOS、Windows、Android、iOS、FreeBSD、OpenBSD和WebAssembly。

data.label: Gio
data.description: Gio is a Go language library for writing cross-platform immediate mode GUIs. Gio supports all major platforms: Linux, macOS, Windows, Android, iOS, FreeBSD, OpenBSD, and WebAssembly.
